      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "I needed a collector to pass to the 2-arg <code>Collectors.groupingBy</code> so that I could map some attribute to arrays of objects per attribute value. This answer gives me exactly that. Also @DidierL."
