      "comment_id" : 114832735,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Since Java 11 the <i>finisher</i> in <i>collectingAndThen</i> can be written as <code>list -&gt; list.toArray(converter)</code> due to addition of <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Collection.html#toArray(java.util.function.IntFunction)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Collection.toArray​(IntFunction)</a>"
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1256567,
      "reputation" : 99,
      "user_id" : 7574723,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/b69d2be3e3ef6d5974bbf1739870f84d?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Thomas Pliakas",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/7574723/thomas-pliakas"
