    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can create a custom collector that convert a stream to array. </p>\n\n<pre><code>public static &lt;T&gt; Collector&lt;T, ?, T[]&gt; toArray( IntFunction&lt;T[]&gt; converter )\n{\n    return Collectors.collectingAndThen( \n                  Collectors.toList(), \n                  list -&gt;list.toArray( converter.apply( list.size() ) ) );\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>and a quick use</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; input = Arrays.asList( ..... );\n\nString[] result = input.stream().\n         .collect( CustomCollectors.**toArray**( String[]::new ) );\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
